description: Barbie I Can Be Teacher Playset: With this playset, girls can explore the role of a teacher, plus have access to additional web content that allows them to further try on the role. Barbie as teacher comes with student Chelsea who raises her left arm when the button in her back is pushed. Lessons can be written in chalk on the real blackboard (which flips to reveal a world map) and erased with the eraser that fits perfectly on Barbie doll's hand. School-themed accessories also include a student desk, scissors, lunchbox and bottle of glue.
